<h2 id="cinnamon-rolls">Cinnamon Rolls</h2>
<p><em>All Cinnamon Rolls are Vegan and Dairy-free created using Almond Milk and Plant-based Oils.</em></p>

<div class="menu-row">
     <img class="menu-img" src="../assets/img/menu-original.jpg" />
     <div class="menu-text">
